<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">Explanation:</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">1^2 + 9^2 = 82</span></span>
